      "properties": {
        "Node name for S&R": "HYWorld_EnvironmentPromptBuilder"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "[\"SCENE 1: Vast labyrinthine underground research facility, brutalist concrete corridors stretching into darkness, fluorescent lights flickering overhead casting harsh shadows, rows of humming server racks and industrial ventilation ducts, distant tremors causing dust to fall from the ceiling, emergency warning lights pulsing amber, cold clinical atmosphere with visible breath condensation, Ridley Scott aesthetic\", \"SCENE 2: High-security biochemistry laboratory, walls of glass containment chambers filled with bioluminescent bacterial cultures glowing sickly green, scattered papers and overturned equipment from a recent emergency, multiple workstations with holographic displays showing mutation data, dramatic chiaroscuro lighting from overhead surgical lamps, tension and chaos frozen in time, Denis Villeneuve color palette\", \"SCENE 3: Narrow emergency access tunnel carved through raw rock, emergency strip lighting along the floor casting deep red upward shadows, exposed pipes dripping condensation, distant echoing footsteps reverberating off metal grating, claustrophobic low ceiling forcing characters to crouch, smoke wisps curling through the air from overloaded electrical systems, atmosphere of desperate urgency and survival\"]",
        60,
        "mistralai/Mistral-Nemo-Instruct-2407",
        "Standard"
      ]
    }
